* Biomass was having a rather good time playing Perndabot for what he was 
worth, crossing his arms over his chest and waiting for Perndabot to make up 
his mind on what his attack would be next.
Nue'e sighs but looks around as 4 more bots come onto the scene, all male. 
Of course.
She crossed her own arms and gave Biomass a glare, only finding that he 
flashed a know-it-all smile at her before smiling in Perndabot's direction.
Biomass's expression was now a preyy happy one, one he was sure would piss 
Perndabot off because the agression in his attetude wasn't getting to him.*

" You're move."

* Nue'e slapped her forehead and pushed her glasses back up the bridge of 
her nose, rolling her eyes.
Must be a male thing.*
